quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  23,33,"Uski qaum ke jin sardaron ne maanne se inkar kiya aur aakhirat ki peshi ko jhutlaya, jinko humne duniya ki zindagi mein aasuda kar rakkha tha, woh kehne lagey “ye shaks kuch nahin hai magar ek bashar tum hi jaisa, jo kuch tum khate ho wahi yeh khata hai aur jo kuch tum peete ho wahi yeh peeta hai"
  23,34,Ab agar tumne apne hi jaise ek bashar ki itaat qabool karli to tum ghatay hi mein rahey
  23,35,Yeh tumhein ittila deta hai ke jab tum mar kar mitti ho jaogey aur haddiyon ka panjar reh jaogey us waqt tum (qabaron se) nikale jaogey
  23,36,"Baeed (far/Impossible), bilkul baeed(Impossible) hai yeh wada jo tumse kiya jaa raha hai"
  23,37,Zindagi kuch nahin hai magar bas yahi duniya ki zindagi. Yahin humko marna aur jeena hai aur hum hargiz uthaye janey waley nahin hain
  23,38,Yeh shaks khuda ke naam par mehaz jhoot ghadh raha hai aur hum kabhi iske maanne waley nahin hain.”
  23,39,"Rasool ne kaha “parwardigar , in logon ne jo meri takzeeb ki hai, ispar ab tu hi meri nusrat farma”"
  23,40,Jawab mein irshad hua “qareeb hai woh waqt jab yeh apne kiye par pachtayenge”
  23,41,Aakhir e kaar theek theek haqq ke mutabiq ek hungama e azeem ne unko aa liya aur humne inko kachra bana kar phenk diya. Door ho zaalim qaum
  23,42,Phir humne unke baad dusri qaumein uthayi
  23,43,Koi qaum na apne waqt se pehle khatam hui aur na uske baad thehar saki
  23,44,"Phir humne pai dar pai apne Rasool bheje. Jis qaum ke paas bhi uska Rasool aaya, usne usey jhutlaya, aur hum ek ke baad ek qaum ko halaak karte chale gaye hatta ke unko bas afsana hi bana kar choda, phitkar un logon par jo iman nahin laatey"
  23,45,Phir humne Moosa aur uske bhai Haroon ko apni nishaniyon aur khuli sanad ke saath Firoun aur uske ayaan sultanat ki taraf bheja
  23,46,Magar unhon ne takabbur (arrogance) kiya aur badi dunki li
  23,47,Kehne lage “Kya hum apne hi jaise do aadmiyon par iman le aayein? Aur aadmi bhi woh jinki qaum hamari bandi (ghulam) hai”
  23,48,Pas unhon ne dono ko jhutla diya aur halaak honay walon mein jaa miley
  23,49,Aur Moosa ko humne kitaab ata farmayi taa-ke log ussey rehnumayi haasil karein
  23,50,Aur Ibne Maryam aur uski maa ko humne ek nishani banaya aur unko ek sateh murtafa (shelter on a plateau) par rakkha jo itminaan ki jagah thi aur chashme usmein jaari thay